The paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the resilience of agents to adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also deals with safe exploration, which is a topic in robotics, falling under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses interruptibility, which is a topic in control systems, falling under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper also deals with AI agents, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
